The paper deals with attribute detection in computer vision, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes to use techniques from multi-source domain generalization, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of attributes for image retrieval (cs.IR) and learning with humans in the loop (cs.MM).
